E4Plus1.uk.description: Gluons, Guacamole, and the Color Purple: Sheldon feels academically unchallenged at school, so he audits a college class taught by his pen pal, Dr John Sturgis. (S1 Ep19/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Young Sheldon
E4Plus1.uk.description: A Dog, a Squirrel, and a Fish Named Fish: A neighbourhood feud erupts between the Coopers and the Sparks family when the Sparks' new dog terrorises Sheldon. (S1 Ep20/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: E My Sports: When Bart starts earning money from video game competitions, Homer becomes his coach, and their team make it to the finals in South Korea. (S30 Ep17/23)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Bart vs. Itchy & Scratchy: Bart's upset about a new, all-girl Itchy and Scratchy. Then he joins an all-girl pranking crew, Bossy Riot. (S30 Ep18/23)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Irish Pub Formulation: A visit from Raj's sister Priya creates tension among the guys, especially when Leonard asks Sheldon to conceal his romantic past with her. (S4 Ep6)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Apology Insufficiency: Leonard thinks his dating problems are due to a lack of confidence, and vows to be self-assured around attractive women. Howard is called by the FBI. (S4 Ep7)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The 21-Second Excitation: The gang's plans to attend a film screening are scuppered by Sheldon's nemesis Wil Wheaton. Penny and Bernadette invite Amy to her first slumber party. (S4 Ep8)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Boyfriend Complexity: When Penny's father visits, Leonard discovers that her parents still think that he and Penny are a couple, so he takes advantage of the situation. (S4 Ep9)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Bart Gets Famous: Thanks to his new catchphrase, 'I didn't do it', Bart becomes famous, getting his own TV series and releasing a range of merchandise. (S5 Ep12/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Homer and Apu: When Apu loses the Kwik-E-Mart, he moves in with the Simpsons. And then Homer joins him on a pilgrimage to the first ever Kwik-E-Mart, in the Himalayas. (S5 Ep13/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Bull-E: Bart is picked on at the school dance, so Marge convinces Springfield's authorities to pass anti-bullying legislation. But then Homer's arrested for victimising Ned. (S26 Ep21/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Mathlete's Feat: Groundskeeper Willie coaches Lisa and the school Mathlympics team for an important maths quiz. (S26 Ep22/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: America's Next Top Model
E4Plus1.uk.description: Lana Marks: The models have all-important meetings with numerous fashion brands across LA, with the best contestants securing a spot on this series' overseas trip, to Morocco. (S16 Ep8)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Mission: Impossible - Rogue Nation
E4Plus1.uk.description: (2015) Part five of the Tom Cruise action-thriller franchise. The secret agents must bring down a terrorist group, but that's not easy when the CIA are hunting you down...

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Closet Reconfiguration: When Howard and Bernadette get Sheldon to organise their untidy closet, Sheldon finds an unopened letter from Howard's long-absent father. (S6 Ep19)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Tenure Turbulence: Leonard, Sheldon, Raj and Kripke all compete for the same vacancy at the university. (S6 Ep20)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Naked Attraction
E4Plus1.uk.description: Rebecca's tired of guys with bad boy images breaking her heart. Dan thinks the only thing missing in his life's the love of a good man. Can they find love the Naked Attraction way? (S1 Ep5)

E4Plus1.uk.title: America's Next Top Model
E4Plus1.uk.description: Highlights and Catfights: A look back at series 16's most dramatic moments - along with some behind-the-scenes footage - before the remaining contestants jet off to Morocco. (S16 Ep9)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Boy-Scoutz 'n the Hood: During an all-syrup Squishee bender, Bart joins the junior campers, and ends up taking the embarrassing - and dangerous - Homer on a river rafting trip. (S5 Ep8/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Young Sheldon
E4Plus1.uk.description: Gluons, Guacamole, and the Color Purple: Sheldon feels academically unchallenged at school, so he audits a college class taught by his pen pal, Dr John Sturgis. (S1 Ep19/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Young Sheldon
E4Plus1.uk.description: A Dog, a Squirrel, and a Fish Named Fish: A neighbourhood feud erupts between the Coopers and the Sparks family when the Sparks' new dog terrorises Sheldon. (S1 Ep20/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Modern Family
E4Plus1.uk.description: Whanex?: While preparing a presentation for his students about future goals, Cam must contend with a bully at the school. Jay has technical trouble during a video conference. (S10 Ep13)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Goldbergs
E4Plus1.uk.description: Stop Arguing and Start Thanking: When Beverly invites Murray's unreliable brother Marvin to visit at Thanksgiving, she reignites their long-standing feud. (S1 Ep9)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Goldbergs
E4Plus1.uk.description: Shopping: Erica's new job at a department store is put in jeopardy when Beverly takes advantage of her daughter's employee discount far too frequently. (S1 Ep10)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Neighborhood
E4Plus1.uk.description: Welcome to the Dream Girls: Tina reunites with her former girl group after decades apart, but old issues threaten their big performance. (S4 Ep21)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Neighborhood
E4Plus1.uk.description: Welcome to the Ring: As Marty prepares to propose to his girlfriend, Calvin and Tina plan a party honouring their future daughter-in-law's Nigerian heritage. (S4 Ep22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Rude(ish) Tube Shorts
E4Plus1.uk.description: A short, cheeky clip from Rude Tube's naughty little sister Rude(ish) Tube, featuring sheep.

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Goldbergs
E4Plus1.uk.description: Man of the House: Erica's graduation is eclipsed by excitement about the new baby. Adam and Barry fight for the title of 'man of the house' in Murray's absence. (S10 Ep4)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Goldbergs
E4Plus1.uk.description: Uncle-ing: Erica asks Geoff to take her on a 'babymoon' to get her far away from Beverly. But then Erica's water breaks and she goes into labour... (S10 Ep5)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Goldbergs
E4Plus1.uk.description: DKNY: Adam visits Dave Kim at NYU to celebrate Halloween. Geoff's fear of Beverly taking over baby care duties turns into a jump-scare-filled comedic thriller. (S10 Ep6)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Goldbergs
E4Plus1.uk.description: Rhinestones and Roses: Beverly embraces her new life as a grandmother while trying to stay young at heart, and Adam gets a job while he waits to start at NYU. (S10 Ep7)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Goldbergs
E4Plus1.uk.description: Another Turkey in the Trot: Adam and Barry are determined to give Beverly a joyous conflict-free Thanksgiving, but their plans go awry. (S10 Ep8)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Dora and the Lost City of Gold
E4Plus1.uk.description: (2019) Family adventure with Isabela Moner, Eva Longoria and Michael Pea. Everyone's favourite young explorer must track down her parents, who are missing in Peru.

E4Plus1.uk.title: Monster House
E4Plus1.uk.description: (2006) Spooky animated caper with Maggie Gyllenhaal and Steve Buscemi. A young boy and his babysitter spy on the creepy neighbour. Did he really eat his wife?

E4Plus1.uk.title: Ramsay's Kitchen Nightmares USA
E4Plus1.uk.description: Zayna Flaming Grill (Part 1/2): Gordon makes the first of two visits to Zayna Flaming Grill, a Mediterranean restaurant in Redondo Beach owned by Faye and her niece Brenda. (S7 Ep6)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Ramsay's Kitchen Nightmares USA
E4Plus1.uk.description: Zayna Flaming Grill (Part 2/2): Gordon returns to California for the conclusion of his challenge to save Zayna Flaming Grill. Can he inject flavour into the tired menu? (S7 Ep7)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Hot Tub Contamination: Leonard and Penny intervene when Sheldon and Amy have an argument. Howard and Bernadette are disturbed by unexpected guests. (S10 Ep5)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Fetal Kick Catalyst: Penny meets her fans at a comic book convention. Sheldon and Amy host brunch at Penny's flat. Howard makes an impulsive purchase. (S10 Ep6)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Veracity Elasticity: Leonard is upset when he finds out that Penny has been moving his collectables out of Sheldon's old room and into storage behind his back. (S10 Ep7)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Brain Bowl Incubation: Sheldon tries to convince Amy that they should procreate. Raj feels embarrassed about what the new woman in his life does for a living. (S10 Ep8)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Great Christmas Bake Off
E4Plus1.uk.description: Merry bakers from Bake Off past - Val, Selasi, Paul and Beca - join Paul, Prue, Noel and Sandi to compete in festive challenges for the title of Star Baker. (Ep1/2)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Beyond Blunderdome: Mel Gibson hires Homer to help him rewrite his remake of Mr Smith Goes to Washington. (S11 Ep1/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: E-I-E-I-(Annoyed Grunt): The Simpsons are forced to flee to the countryside, where Homer accidentally invents highly addictive tomacco. But the animals like it too... (S11 Ep5/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Last Temptation of Homer: Homer falls for his beautiful new colleague Mindy Simmons (guest star Michelle Pfeiffer), who shares his love of doughnuts... (S5 Ep9/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: $pringfield (or How I Learned to Stop Worrying and Love Legalized Gambling): Homer gets a job at Mr Burns' new casino and Marge gets addicted to the slot machines. (S5 Ep10/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Homer the Vigilante: Homer sets up a chaotic vigilante group to combat one-man crime spree Molloy (guest star Sam Neill). (S5 Ep11/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Bart Gets Famous: Thanks to his new catchphrase, 'I didn't do it', Bart becomes famous, getting his own TV series and releasing a range of merchandise. (S5 Ep12/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Homer and Apu: When Apu loses the Kwik-E-Mart, he moves in with the Simpsons. And then Homer joins him on a pilgrimage to the first ever Kwik-E-Mart, in the Himalayas. (S5 Ep13/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Gogglebox Festive Special
E4Plus1.uk.description: On the Christmas box: Michael McIntyre's Christmas Wheel, First Dates at Christmas, Strictly the Real Full Monty, Love Actually, World's Strongest Man, Elves, and No Time to Die.

E4Plus1.uk.title: Gogglebox
E4Plus1.uk.description: This time on the 'Box: Eurovision Song Contest, Bridgerton, Love Triangle Australia, Double the Money, Marcus Wareing Simply Provence and BBC News (northern lights). (S23 Ep14) [SL]
